text: Yusuf Zuayyin (; 1931 - 10 January 2016) was a Syrian politician. He was a member of the Ba'ath Party. He served as Prime Minister from 1965 and, again, from 1966 to 1968. He was born in Al-Bukamal. Zuayyin died after a long illness on 10 January 2016 in Stockholm, Sweden.
